Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.47,0:00:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卫 求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.40,0:00:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请转过来看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.91,0:00:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是将抹不去的爱意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.61,0:00:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下一下地结起来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.22,0:00:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于做成的许愿腕带
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.70,0:00:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然践踏少女的纯情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.26,0:00:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.12,0:00:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我水手月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.73,0:00:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代表月亮 惩罚你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.09,0:01:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.29,0:02:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.90,0:02:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.62,0:02:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.58,0:02:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.08,0:02:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.73,0:02:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 课外活动怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.33,0:02:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天春菜老师休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.59,0:02:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这一小时左右大家自习
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.50,0:02:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.30,0:02:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是再吃上一碗饭就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海野 还给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.66,0:02:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.34,0:02:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好好做完再给你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.45,0:02:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.77,0:02:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈留这么说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.25,0:02:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 什么呀什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.75,0:02:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许愿腕带啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.11,0:02:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.80,0:02:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兔同学 你不知道许愿腕带吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.30,0:02:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,职业摔跤？(日语发音相近）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.95,0:02:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我上了 哦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.72,0:02:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好猥琐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.96,0:02:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.42,0:03:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0){\fn方正粗圆_GBK}{\fs45}{\pos(320,450)}{\b0}{\1c&HD7FFFF&}{\4c&HFFC1C1&}{\shad1}{\bord0}相同的感觉！小兔和卫的爱再燃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.14,0:03:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是传说中的许愿腕带哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.14,0:03:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好可爱呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派什么用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.71,0:03:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将两根腕带倾注着愿望编在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.98,0:03:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴在手腕或脚脖子上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.06,0:03:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.72,0:03:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是当它断开的时候愿望就会实现哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.60,0:03:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在全国都在流行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.01,0:03:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.84,0:03:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.12,0:03:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知什么时候大家都在做了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.18,0:03:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是也来做做看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据愿望的不同 打结的方式也各式各样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 这次十番街上也开了专卖店呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.08,0:03:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绣花线 教材 皮绳 装饰彩珠等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.86,0:03:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对应许愿腕带的必要东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.35,0:03:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了在那里一应俱全外
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.43,0:03:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,针对买了材料的人还开了免费讲座呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.47,0:04:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为男友编制作为礼物的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.88,0:04:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二人的关系就能长久地进行下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.13,0:04:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我和奈留一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.02,0:04:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…那我也
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.59,0:04:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.69,0:04:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再对我这么亲密了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.86,0:04:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你已经感觉不到爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让我再重复了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.17,0:04:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请回去吧 回去！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.30,0:04:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不是说要永远永远在一起的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.91,0:04:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.32,0:04:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.24,0:04:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.61,0:04:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.03,0:04:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无精打彩的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.20,0:04:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是在学校发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.30,0:04:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没这回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.06,0:05:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就打起精神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.06,0:05:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有什么烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.44,0:05:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候都可以来找我们说的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.56,0:05:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.73,0:05:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过真的没什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了对了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.09,0:05:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这阵子在十番街呀 有许愿腕带的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.82,0:05:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.62,0:05:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.57,0:05:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然如我所愿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.97,0:05:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到小卫了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.89,0:05:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.56,0:05:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.94,0:05:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.17,0:05:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我至今一直在想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却怎么也不明白为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.22,0:05:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.21,0:05:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变得讨厌我了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.38,0:05:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无论如何也不能象这样放弃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.34,0:05:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 至少把原因告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.43,0:05:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为我的自私 请原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.15,0:06:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.56,0:06:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.95,0:06:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵呵呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.86,0:06:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一族的王子狄曼特啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲜红的红酒已经充满了美丽的水晶东京了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.59,0:06:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着 我要将这个乱七八糟的东京
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.03,0:06:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用黑暗能量填满
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的负点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.57,0:06:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.29,0:07:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泥土妖 腕带
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腕带
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.39,0:07:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个东京真是又挤又闷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.38,0:07:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点让黑暗阵石的能量成长起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.09,0:07:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解 带子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.75,0:07:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狄曼特拉大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.58,0:07:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想快点回到你那边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.89,0:07:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后一头钻进你的怀里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是现在很热门的美参贺馆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.67,0:07:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许愿腕带是幸福的记号哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能实现愿望的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.95,0:07:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.30,0:07:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道一定能使你幸福的护身符是什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个护身符呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信任是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.23,0:07:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信任的力量可以唤来幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.77,0:07:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 我也是在书上看的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.18,0:08:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过呀 我觉得信任的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.26,0:08:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能让自己打起精神来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.62,0:08:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 谢谢你 真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.83,0:08:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.63,0:08:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是修复恋人关系的许愿腕带的制作材料哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.90,0:08:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.25,0:08:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 教室就在这边了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.35,0:08:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 我们就在那边了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.61,0:08:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.76,0:08:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是新来的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.55,0:08:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.62,0:08:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.26,0:08:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈留 海野
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友吗 那请坐到这边的位子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天无精打彩的让我很担心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.26,0:08:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个腕带呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.94,0:08:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请全部剪成90厘米的长度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.10,0:08:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要十条哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.81,0:08:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.65,0:08:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先用胶带纸把线全部固定在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.73,0:08:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后从中间开始象书写“四”一样编织
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.21,0:08:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复两次以上动作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.51,0:08:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 从中间开始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还是从比较简单的样式开始做起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.74,0:09:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.54,0:09:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用全部六根线从左开始象“四”字形编织
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.50,0:09:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 这样可就非常简单了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.14,0:09:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是谁一开始都不能顺利做好的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么今天的课程就到这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.77,0:09:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位同学回到家以后要好好看看教材哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.14,0:09:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 还要看书 真麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.99,0:09:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白了吗！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.67,0:09:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.71,0:09:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师再见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢老师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.73,0:09:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么各位回家路上请小心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦咧 哦咧 哦咧 腕带！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.23,0:09:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腕带 作战进行的怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:09:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚那些戴着腕带的人会被污染 圈圈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.67,0:10:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后黑暗能量一口气加速
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.59,0:10:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗阵石就会成长起来了 圈圈 圈圈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.66,0:10:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你让我很期待哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.49,0:10:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许愿腕带完成了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.68,0:10:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家也好想做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.07,0:10:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做不习惯的事做累了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.48,0:10:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们让她一个人待一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.82,0:10:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卫 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.72,0:10:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卫 我们终于能结婚了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.32,0:10:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兔 再也不会离开你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.88,0:10:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.73,0:10:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.75,0:11:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.38,0:11:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.51,0:11:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地场卫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.51,0:11:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兔！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.84,0:11:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能接近月野兔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.88,0:11:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.32,0:11:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当你们两人结合时
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.86,0:11:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界就会毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.47,0:11:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月野兔也就是倩尼迪公主就会遭遇不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.96,0:11:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗…骗人的 骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.51,0:11:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦…梦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.97,0:11:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会做这种梦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.45,0:11:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小卫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.90,0:11:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.80,0:12:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卫 小卫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.57,0:12:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 你以为现在几点了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.26,0:12:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卫 我无论如何有事想问你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.57,0:12:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我没什么好说的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.98,0:12:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.90,0:12:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.92,0:12:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卫也做过那个奇怪的梦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.62,0:12:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的梦！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.84,0:12:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兔怎么突然跑去小卫家了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.55,0:12:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她应该好好编完的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.47,0:12:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 小兔也做了和我一样的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.04,0:12:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.97,0:12:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那也许只是个梦而已不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 小兔说不定也会死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.33,0:12:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卫 为了我你才特意对我这么冷淡是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.57,0:12:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那种梦我才不会相信的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.98,0:12:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一开始也不相信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.28,0:12:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 每晚每晚都是同样的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.38,0:13:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不仅仅 不仅仅是个普通的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是个预言未来发生的事的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.06,0:13:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.99,0:13:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要和小卫在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死也没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.17,0:13:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.21,0:13:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 我们还是不可以在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.98,0:13:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.72,0:13:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卫！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.67,0:13:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是地球毁灭了 我死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.11,0:13:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是想和小卫…和小卫在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.46,0:13:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.24,0:13:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小卫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说没用的话了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.74,0:13:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开门啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.43,0:13:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.44,0:13:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兔真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.23,0:13:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.81,0:13:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.47,0:13:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 小小兔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.95,0:13:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从手上拿不下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.87,0:14:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小兔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.73,0:14:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小兔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.07,0:14:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小兔 不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.71,0:14:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.63,0:14:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露娜 发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.49,0:14:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许愿腕带突然就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.21,0:14:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.02,0:14:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.33,0:14:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露娜 小小兔就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.45,0:14:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.03,0:14:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿…拿不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救…救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.92,0:14:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海野
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.63,0:14:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.30,0:14:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.54,0:14:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那家新开的许愿腕带店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.65,0:14:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上赶来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.44,0:14:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚提密斯 我们走！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.11,0:14:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.47,0:14:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.96,0:14:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:03.94,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF66FF&}月水晶力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,0:15:05.90,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF66FF&}变身
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.80,0:15:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗黑力量再提高更多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.71,0:15:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带子 带子 带子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.05,0:15:55.14,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF66FF&}我不会让你那样做的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.20,0:15:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何方神圣 圈圈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.81,0:15:59.38,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF66FF&}居然对着别人将愿望倾注在带子里的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.67,0:16:01.13,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF66FF&}希望实现的梦想泼冷水
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.58,0:16:03.44,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF66FF&}而且还将少女的信任之心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.66,0:16:05.96,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF66FF&}用邪恶的能量污染 不可原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.35,0:16:10.05,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF66FF&}爱与正义的水手服美少女战士
