Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.37,0:16:16.36,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF66FF&}代表月亮惩罚你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.13,0:16:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没规矩
