Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.27,0:16:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二环攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.46,0:16:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对没有男友的你来说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.03,0:16:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心形可真是再合适不过了 圈圈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.83,0:16:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真失礼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.07,0:16:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然看我这样 男朋友的话还是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.45,0:16:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水手月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.73,0:16:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.27,0:16:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.12,0:16:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真轻松 接下来就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.78,0:17:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圈圈 圈圈 圈圈…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.28,0:17:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么人 圈圈！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.48,0:17:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许愿腕带是希望之环
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.15,0:17:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用美丽少女的信赖干坏事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.21,0:17:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内心丑恶的恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.85,0:17:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我夜礼服假面 绝不原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.26,0:17:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵呵 信赖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.24,0:17:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真 太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.66,0:17:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是天大的笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.41,0:17:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三环雷击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.01,0:17:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是专门对你这种想交朋友的人
